.NET Core 1.0.name: DiscordVoiceClient
.NET Core 1.0.summary: An interface for interacting with a voice connection to Discord.

methods.name: CanSendVoiceData(int size)
methods.summary: Gets whether or not the specified number of bytes can be queued in this DiscordVoiceClient.

methods.name: Disconnect()
FlushVoiceBuffer()
methods.summary: Signals that this DiscordVoiceClient should send all remaining queued audio without worrying about the speaking state or pre-buffering.

methods.name: SendVoiceData(Byte[] data, int offset, int count)
methods.summary: Queues a section of PCM voice data to be sent.
methods.remarks: Should be used along side CanSendVoiceData to ensure the voice buffer is not overflowed.

exceptions.value: Thrown if the number of bytes to be queued would exceed the buffer size of this DiscordVoiceClient.

params.value: The array of voice data to read from.
Where to start reading from the voice data array.
How many bytes to read from the voice data array.

methods.syntax: public void SendVoiceData(Byte[] data, int offset, int count)
methods.linkedSyntax: public void SendVoiceData(Byte[] data, int offset, int count)

methods.name: SetSpeaking(bool speaking)
methods.summary: Sets the speaking state of the GuildMember. Must be set to true for this DiscordVoiceClient to send any voice data.
methods.remarks: Safe to use before this DiscordVoiceClient is fully connected, the last set speaking state will be set upon connecting.

events.name: OnConnected
events.summary: Called when this DiscordVoiceClient finishes connecting to Discord.

events.name: OnDisposed
events.summary: Called when this DiscordVoiceClient is disposed and is no longer valid.

properties.name: BytesToSend
properties.summary: Current number of queued bytes not yet sent.

properties.name: Guild
properties.summary: The DiscordGuild this voice client is connected to.

properties.name: IsConnected
properties.summary: Gets whether or not this DiscordVoiceClient is connected to a DiscordGuild.

properties.name: IsValid
properties.summary: Gets whether or not this DiscordVoiceClient is available to use.
